{"data":{"page":{"id":"6ac1aa64-75ab-5935-a69c-b8decd0ed33e","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/fa22a9fd530f1183689a3ee1d952c382/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>QRCube is a trivial game that uses QR Codes to trigger the questions. It’s built using a custom template (50x50x50 mm) that you need to print and glue to form a cube.</p>\n<p>Each side has a QR Code with a different color and represents a team or a player. Each team has to throw the cube by turns and scan the code on top. After scanning, you get redirected to a URL with a random question for the team whose color corresponds to the code scanned.</p>\n<p>The app allows the players and teams to signup (to create their own QR code) and join the game and also keeps track of the correct/failed answers.</p>\n<p>UPDATE: Sorry, I wasn’t able to upload the source code yet, as  it is currently mixed with other business logic.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2012"},"frontmatter":{"title":"QRCube game","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/cbce3dd788d0cd0d06403bb7db39dcd5/d927d/logo.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/qrcube/","source":"work"}}